  {
    "name": "an ink-smudged scroll",
    "shortName": "scroll",
    "description": "Rolled neatly, this scroll is heavily smudged with various inks. Heavily ingrained fingerprints stain the surface and colour the parchment. Showing signs of wear and tear, the once-sharp sharp corners are now bent, while several of the edges show tiny splits from constant use.",
    "tags": ["writable"],
    "notes": "",
    "interactions": [
      {
        "command": "",
        "response": "",
